description: Smallest cube that begins with n.
links: T. D. Noe, Table of n, a(n) for n=1..1000
mathematica: a[n_] := For[idn = IntegerDigits[n]; k = 1, True, k++, idk = IntegerDigits[k^3]; If[Length[idn] <= Length[idk], If[idk[[1 ;; Length[idn]]] == idn, Return[k^3]]]]; Table[an = a[n]; Print["a(", n, ") = ", an]; an, {n, 1, 1000}] (* _Jean-FranÃ§ois Alcover_, Mar 13 2016 *)
